## NBT

---



[Block Condition Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/block_condition_types/nbt)

Checks the NBT of the block entity.

Type ID: `origins:nbt`




---

### Examples

```json
"block_condition": {
    "type": "origins:and",
    "conditions": [
        {
            "type": "origins:block",
            "block": "minecraft:beacon"
        },
        {
            "type": "origins:nbt",
            "nbt": "{Levels: 1}"
        }
    ]
}
```

This example will check if Beacon block has a `Level` value of 1.

